Title: GitHub Universe Day 1 Keynote recap: Agent HQ, Mission Control, and more
Author: GitHub
Description:
Missed the GitHub Universe Day 1 keynote? We've got you covered. This recap covers the biggest announcements, including Agent HQ bringing agents from OpenAI, Google, Anthropic, and more into GitHub, plus the new Mission Control dashboard, Plan Mode in VS Code, and Custom Agents.
